        And A table is visible with following headers
            | headers             |
            | #                   |
            | Arm name            |
            | Branch name         |
            | Short name          |
            | Cohort name         |
            | Cohort code         |
            | Random. group       |
            | Random. Code        |
            | No. of participants |
            | Modified            |
